---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Disclaimer — Chert Coin" description="Important disclaimers and risk disclosures for Chert Coin network and digital assets.">
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="relative pt-32 pb-16 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 grid-pattern opacity-50"></div>
    <div class="absolute top-1/4 left-1/3 w-[400px] h-[400px] bg-nebula/5 rounded-full blur-[120px]"></div>
    
    <div class="relative max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <span class="inline-block text-nebula-bright font-display text-sm tracking-[0.3em] uppercase mb-4">Legal</span>
        <h1 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-snow mb-6">Disclaimer</h1>
        <p class="text-silver">Last updated: December 7, 2025</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Important Notice -->
  <section class="relative pb-8">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12">
      <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-quantum/10 to-nebula/10 border border-quantum/30 rounded-2xl p-8">
        <div class="flex items-start space-x-4">
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-quantum" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 9v2m0 4h.01m-6.938 4h13.856c1.54 0 2.502-1.667 1.732-3L13.732 4c-.77-1.333-2.694-1.333-3.464 0L3.34 16c-.77 1.333.192 3 1.732 3z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-display text-lg font-bold text-quantum mb-2">Important Notice</h3>
            <p class="text-pearl/80 leading-relaxed">
              This document contains important information about the risks associated with digital assets and blockchain technology. Please read this disclaimer carefully before using any Chert Coin services or acquiring any CHERT tokens.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Content Section -->
  <section class="relative pb-24">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-12">
      <div class="prose prose-invert prose-lg max-w-none">
        
        <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-8 lg:p-12 mb-8">
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-snow mb-6">1. No Financial Advice</h2>
          <p class="text-pearl/80 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            <strong class="text-quantum">NOTHING CONTAINED ON THIS WEBSITE OR IN ANY CHERT COIN MATERIALS CONSTITUTES INVESTMENT, LEGAL, TAX, OR OTHER ADVICE.</strong>
          </p>
          <p class="text-pearl/80 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            The information provided is for general informational purposes only. You should consult with qualified professionals before making any financial decisions. We do not:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-pearl/80 space-y-2">
            <li>Provide investment advice or recommendations</li>
            <li>Guarantee any investment returns or outcomes</li>
            <li>Offer tax, legal, or accounting guidance</li>
            <li>Make any representations about the future value of CHERT tokens</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-8 lg:p-12 mb-8">
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-snow mb-6">2. Risk Disclosure</h2>
          <p class="text-pearl/80 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Digital assets and blockchain technology involve significant risks. By using our services or acquiring CHERT tokens, you acknowledge and accept the following risks:
          </p>
          
          <h3 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-snow mt-6 mb-4">2.1 Market Volatility</h3>
          <p class="text-pearl/80 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            The price of digital assets, including CHERT, can be extremely volatile. Prices may fluctuate significantly in short periods. You could lose all or a substantial portion of your investment.
          </p>

          <h3 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-snow mt-6 mb-4">2.2 Technology Risks</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-pearl/80 space-y-2 mb-4">
            <li><strong class="text-snow">Software Vulnerabilities:</strong> Despite rigorous testing, blockchain software may contain bugs or vulnerabilities</li>
            <li><strong class="text-snow">Smart Contract Risks:</strong> Errors in smart contracts can lead to loss of funds</li>
            <li><strong class="text-snow">Network Attacks:</strong> The network could be subject to hacking, 51% attacks, or other malicious activities</li>
            <li><strong class="text-snow">Consensus Failures:</strong> Consensus mechanisms may fail under certain conditions</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-snow mt-6 mb-4">2.3 Regulatory Uncertainty</h3>
          <p class="text-pearl/80 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            The regulatory landscape for digital assets is evolving and uncertain. Changes in laws or regulations could materially affect the value, functionality, or legality of CHERT tokens. You may be required to comply with local laws that could restrict or prohibit your use of the services.
          </p>

          <h3 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-snow mt-6 mb-4">2.4 Loss of Access</h3>
          <p class="text-pearl/80 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            If you lose access to your private keys, wallet, or recovery phrase, your CHERT tokens will be permanently inaccessible. There is no recovery mechanism for lost private keys in a decentralized system.
          </p>

          <h3 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold text-snow mt-6 mb-4">2.5 Third-Party Risks</h3>
          <p class="text-pearl/80 leading-relaxed">
            Interactions with third-party services, exchanges, bridges, or DeFi protocols carry their own risks. We are not responsible for losses incurred through third-party services.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-8 lg:p-12 mb-8">
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-snow mb-6">3. No Warranties</h2>
          <p class="text-pearl/80 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            THE CHERT COIN NETWORK, SERVICES, AND ALL RELATED MATERIALS ARE PROVIDED "AS IS" AND "AS AVAILABLE" WITHOUT WARRANTIES OF ANY KIND, WHETHER EXPRESS, IMPLIED, STATUTORY, OR OTHERWISE, INCLUDING:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-pearl/80 space-y-2">
            <li>Warranties of merchantability</li>
            <li>Warranties of fitness for a particular purpose</li>
            <li>Warranties of non-infringement</li>
            <li>Warranties of accuracy, reliability, or completeness</li>
            <li>Warranties of uninterrupted or error-free operation</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-8 lg:p-12 mb-8">
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-snow mb-6">4. Forward-Looking Statements</h2>
          <p class="text-pearl/80 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Our website, whitepaper, and other materials may contain forward-looking statements regarding:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-pearl/80 space-y-2 mb-4">
            <li>Future development plans and roadmap</li>
            <li>Expected features and functionality</li>
            <li>Performance projections and targets</li>
            <li>Market adoption and growth estimates</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-pearl/80 leading-relaxed">
            These statements are based on current expectations and assumptions, which may prove to be incorrect. Actual results may differ materially from those expressed or implied. We undertake no obligation to update forward-looking statements.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-8 lg:p-12 mb-8">
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-snow mb-6">5. Token Classification</h2>
          <p class="text-pearl/80 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            CHERT tokens are intended to function as a utility token within the Chert network ecosystem. CHERT tokens:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-pearl/80 space-y-2 mb-4">
            <li>Are not securities, shares, or equity interests</li>
            <li>Do not represent ownership in any legal entity</li>
            <li>Do not entitle holders to dividends or profits</li>
            <li>Do not guarantee any rights beyond network utility</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-pearl/80 leading-relaxed">
            However, regulatory classification may vary by jurisdiction. You are responsible for determining the legal status of CHERT tokens in your jurisdiction.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-8 lg:p-12 mb-8">
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-snow mb-6">6. Geographic Restrictions</h2>
          <p class="text-pearl/80 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            The services and CHERT tokens may not be available in all jurisdictions. By using our services, you confirm that:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-pearl/80 space-y-2">
            <li>You are not located in, or a citizen or resident of, any jurisdiction where such services would be illegal</li>
            <li>You are not subject to economic sanctions or trade restrictions</li>
            <li>You will comply with all applicable local laws and regulations</li>
            <li>You accept sole responsibility for determining the legality of your use</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-8 lg:p-12 mb-8">
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-snow mb-6">7. Experimental Technology</h2>
          <p class="text-pearl/80 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Chert Coin incorporates novel and experimental technologies, including:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-pearl/80 space-y-2 mb-4">
            <li><strong class="text-snow">Alluvium/Tephra/Crystallite/Lithification/Cali Stack:</strong> Advanced layered architecture for batching, ordering, execution, proof packaging, and recovery</li>
            <li><strong class="text-snow">Post-Quantum Cryptography:</strong> NIST-approved quantum-resistant algorithms</li>
            <li><strong class="text-snow">Proof of Useful Work:</strong> Novel mining mechanism integrating scientific computation</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-pearl/80 leading-relaxed">
            These technologies, while rigorously designed, have not been tested at scale in production environments for extended periods. Unknown issues may emerge.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-8 lg:p-12 mb-8">
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-snow mb-6">8. Tax Implications</h2>
          <p class="text-pearl/80 leading-relaxed">
            The acquisition, holding, transfer, staking, or disposal of CHERT tokens may have tax implications in your jurisdiction. You are solely responsible for determining and fulfilling any applicable tax obligations. We recommend consulting with a qualified tax professional regarding your specific situation.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-8 lg:p-12 mb-8">
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-snow mb-6">9. Limitation of Liability</h2>
          <p class="text-pearl/80 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            TO THE MAXIMUM EXTENT PERMITTED BY APPLICABLE LAW, CHERT COIN AND ITS AFFILIATES, DIRECTORS, EMPLOYEES, CONTRIBUTORS, AND AGENTS SHALL NOT BE LIABLE FOR ANY DAMAGES WHATSOEVER, INCLUDING BUT NOT LIMITED TO:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-pearl/80 space-y-2 mb-4">
            <li>Direct, indirect, incidental, special, consequential, or punitive damages</li>
            <li>Loss of profits, revenue, data, or use</li>
            <li>Business interruption or loss of business opportunity</li>
            <li>Any losses arising from your use of the services or tokens</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-pearl/80 leading-relaxed">
            This limitation applies regardless of whether the damages are claimed under contract, tort, negligence, strict liability, or any other legal theory.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-8 lg:p-12 mb-8">
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-snow mb-6">10. Your Responsibility</h2>
          <p class="text-pearl/80 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            By using our services or acquiring CHERT tokens, you acknowledge that you:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-pearl/80 space-y-2">
            <li>Have read and understood this Disclaimer in its entirety</li>
            <li>Accept all risks described herein and any other risks not specifically mentioned</li>
            <li>Have conducted your own independent research and due diligence</li>
            <li>Are not relying on any representations or statements made by Chert Coin</li>
            <li>Have the financial ability to bear the risk of total loss of your investment</li>
            <li>Will seek independent professional advice where appropriate</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="glass rounded-2xl p-8 lg:p-12 mb-8">
          <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-snow mb-6">11. Contact</h2>
          <p class="text-pearl/80 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            If you have questions about this Disclaimer, please contact:
          </p>
          <ul class="text-pearl/80 space-y-2">
            <li><strong class="text-snow">Email:</strong> legal@chert.network</li>
            <li><strong class="text-snow">Discord:</strong> discord.gg/chert</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Acknowledgment Box -->
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-void to-obsidian border border-white/10 rounded-2xl p-8 mt-12">
          <p class="text-center text-silver text-sm leading-relaxed">
            By using Chert Coin services or acquiring CHERT tokens, you acknowledge that you have read, understood, and agree to be bound by this Disclaimer, our <a href="/terms" class="text-quantum hover:text-quantum-bright underline">Terms of Service</a>, and our <a href="/privacy" class="text-silica-bright hover:text-silica underline">Privacy Policy</a>.
          </p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .prose h2 {
    margin-top: 0;
  }
  
  .prose h3 {
    color: var(--color-snow);
  }
  
  .prose ul {
    margin-left: 0;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
  }
  
  .prose li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
</style>
